A Place In The Sun's Danni Menzies put her toned figure on display in a new picture shared with her 99,000 Instagram followers. The presenter has been enjoying the sunshine in the popular Greek holiday hotspot Mykonos. Taking to her Instagram Story, Danni shared a picture of herself laying on the floor in a bikini while soaking up the sun. The sultry shot puts Danni’s slender figure on display as she gazes out into the sea. She also shared an insight into her trip on her main feed, with a video of herself practising yoga atop a mountain. The clip showcased the stunning ocean views she was enjoying while stretching and contorting her body. The TV star captioned the mesmerising post: “Morning flow in the most special spot.”